      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-1"><gap/><gap/><gap/><gap/><hi rend="display-initial">D</hi>Eaf, giddy, helpless, left alone,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-2"> To all my friends a burden grown;</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-3"> No more I hear my church's bell,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-4"> Than if it rung for my own knell:</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-5"> At thunder now no more I start,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-6"> Than at the rumbling of a cart;</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-7"> And what's incredible, alack!</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-673A44PJ-line-8"> No more I hear a woman's clack.673A44PJ   </l></lg></div>
